title: Convert Meters per Second to Kilometers per Hour
description:
MS_TO_KMH calculates a speed value of meters/second to kilometers/hour 
to.
MS_TO_KMH := MS * 3.6
name: MS_TO_KMH

input.name: ms
input.description: The velocity in meters per second.

return_value.description: The converted velocity in kilometers per hour.
